  "title": "Mighty Smoky Ukrainian Sausages Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and smoky stew featuring Italian fennel sausages and a mirepoix base, perfect for a cold winter's night. This dish is dense and adventurous, with a raw-friendly twist.",
