  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced Italian fennel sausages and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Remove the sausages from the pot and set aside.",
    "Add the chopped onions, carrots, and celery to the pot and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic to the pot and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the smoked paprika, chicken broth, dried thyme, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Return the sausages to the pot and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
